{"tid":14974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"關於高登同此apps，我想講嘅係","createTime":"2016-11-30T17:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T19:41:13.000Z","uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d467e6c976d2b8e08feb9a00d4f248e3e8ffd271","tid":14974,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:45:33.000Z","msg":"大家無謂再屌高登，過咗去嘅就過咗去。其實邊度都好，都只係一個平台，俾大家講下笑下交流下。好似icq msn whatsapp咁，大家唔會出新嘢就屌舊嘢有幾衰加嘛。既然依家大家覺得有個新嘅地方係更好嘅，咪過嚟囉。舊嘅經唔起考驗自然會被淘汰。大家只需要monitor住呢度，唔好俾外人嚟搞事，唔好俾呢度越變越差，就ok啦。<br />\n<br />\n高登始終係一個回憶，無論佢最後變到幾唔好，大家都唔應該忘記，當初嘅我哋，都係喺嗰度大嫁。"},{"pid":"1039dc8e23293e64e98737b88c392a60d03f9997","tid":14974,"uid":6842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:49:08.000Z","msg":"講多句。其實大家鍾意嘅唔係高登，係喺嗰度創立嘅一套文化。呢樣嘢可以轉移到另一個更方便嘅平台係好事嚟。但都係嗰句，大家唔可以忘本。"},{"pid":"2bb7de96ce481fd7f54710fa1bf0931f4680ba6f","tid":14974,"uid":33797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:49:19.000Z","msg":"未解決.jpg"},{"pid":"2bbf0b25399dce9cb13642bedd4de4c994f8ec02","tid":14974,"uid":35822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T17:55:21.000Z","msg":"係屌早洩經營不善啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12bfe2bf6c719d9e1d596eaa18fce41eeee4ba5","tid":14974,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:26:26.000Z","msg":"唔希望失去左高登既文化，<br />\n<br />\n唔想係到再見到5p字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf087a22a3d13c84edd6b113afec24a6dd2b300a","tid":14974,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:52:10.000Z","msg":"只係唔上方丈個高登姐<br />\n唔代表放棄高登文化"},{"pid":"c580f4d3db0bf2fc245a90ed721ee11d560a7722","tid":14974,"uid":582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T18:53:09.000Z","msg":"從來都係屌緊某人管理不善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cee1eec9d2f300c34ab264cfeb08f0934e9e0d0","tid":14974,"uid":17510,"l